{#
name: Task Scheduler
description: Schedule tasks with dependencies and execution order
tags: [workflow, schedule, tasks, dependencies]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of scheduling purpose
    required: true
  - name: schedule_type
    type: str
    description: Schedule type (cron, interval, manual)
    default: cron
  - name: tasks
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated task names or IDs
    required: true
  - name: dependencies
    type: str
    description: Task dependencies (e.g. "b->a,c->b" means b depends on a)
    default: ""
examples:
  - "Schedule report generation with dependency: fetch -> aggregate -> send"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: workflow
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 调度配置

- 类型：{{ schedule_type }}
- 任务：{{ tasks }}
- 依赖：{{ dependencies }}

## 执行逻辑

1. 按 dependencies 解析执行顺序
2. 无依赖任务并行执行
3. 依赖满足后触发下游任务

## 注意事项

- dependencies 格式：task_id->dep_id 或留空表示无依赖
- schedule_type 决定触发方式
